<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="mirror-vt">mirror <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'mɪrə(r)/    美 /'mɪrər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-reflect">1.★ <strong>反映；映照 (reflect)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a TV play that mirrors modern society 
反映现代社会的电视剧</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The trees were mirrored in the still water of the lake.
树木倒映在静静的湖水中。</p></div></div>